odanog... Taksi!
Malo luckast, malo zločest,

265
00:23:14,440 --> 00:23:18,120
Ali to cure zapravo vole, ha,

266
00:23:19,920 --> 00:23:25,080
<i>Što je? Maca papala jezika?
- Zaboravio sam...</i>

267
00:23:26,360 --> 00:23:28,880
Ideš ili ne ideš?

268
00:23:48,440 --> 00:23:50,680
Razumiješ li?

269
00:23:50,840 --> 00:23:54,040
Očekujem da budeš nježan
i pažIjiv Ijubavnik,

270
00:23:54,240 --> 00:23:56,960
Plemenit, ali
čvrst, - Što...?

271
00:23:57,120 --> 00:24:00,200
Lznevjeriš li ta
razumna očekivanja,

272
00:24:00,360 --> 00:24:03,920
od seksa neće biti ni S!

273
00:24:04,480 --> 00:24:06,600
Dobro?

274
00:24:17,920 --> 00:24:19,920
Diane...

275
00:24:20,400 --> 00:24:23,400
Što... - Tiho!

276
00:25:01,760 --> 00:25:04,160
Probudi se, Spud!

277
00:25:04,320 --> 00:25:06,000
Probudi se,

278
00:25:06,160 --> 00:25:08,080
Seks!

279
00:25:08,680 --> 00:25:11,000
Usputan seks,

280
00:25:17,480 --> 00:25:20,560
Tommy... Pusti snimku, - Sada?

281
00:25:21,160 --> 00:25:24,040
Da se gledamo
dok se ševimo,

282
00:25:24,240 --> 00:25:26,800
Da vidim što propuštam,

283
00:25:40,160 --> 00:25:42,840
Ne mnogo!

284
00:25:43,840 --> 00:25:47,960
<i>Kapetan Archie Gemmill
kreće izvana...</i>

285
00:25:48,520 --> 00:25:51,360
<i>Želi se sam probiti,</i>

286
00:25:51,640 --> 00:25:54,920
<i>Uspjet će! Juri prema
vratima, Zgoditak!</i>

287
00:25:55,160 --> 00:25:58,920
<i>Divna li zgoditka!
Gemmill je u punoj formi!</i>

288
00:25:59,320 --> 00:26:02,680
<i>Razvalio je mrežu!</i>

289
00:26:03,200 --> 00:26:07,760
Ovako mi je bilo kad smo
'78, pobijedili Nizozemsku!

290
00:26:11,200 --> 00:26:14,200
Ne možeš tu spavati, Odlazi,

291
00:26:14,760 --> 00:26:19,640
Ma daj! - Spavaj u hodniku,
ili idi doma, Izaberi sam,

292
00:26:21,440 --> 00:26:25,680
I budi tih, - Isuse!

293
00:26:32,480 --> 00:26:37,000
<i>Kako nema je?! Gdje je?!
- Mora biti tu negdje,</i>

294
00:26:39,560 --> 00:26:42,760
Možda sam je zabunom
vratio, - Vratio?!

295
00:26:43,000 --> 00:26:45,960
Kamo? U videoteku?!

296
00:26:46,120 --> 00:26:48,920
U jebenu videoteku?!

297
00:26:49,120 --> 00:26:53,240
Da svi kreteni mogu
drkati na našu snimku?!

298
00:26:54,080 --> 00:26:57,520
Isuse! Zlo mi je!

299
00:27:29,040 --> 00:27:32,040
Bok, - Zdravo,

300
00:28:14,000 --> 00:28:16,320
Izvoli sjesti,

301
00:28:16,480 --> 00:28:19,240
Hoćeš kave? - Aha,

302
00:28:20,640 --> 00:28:23,280
Ti si Mark? - Taj sam,

303
00:28:28,680 --> 00:28:33,080
Dianin prijatelj?
- Prijateljev prijatelj,

304
00:28:35,520 --> 00:28:37,960
Vi ste joj cimeri?

305
00:28:39,000 --> 00:28:42,440
Cimeri?! Dobra fora,

306
00:28:44,120 --> 00:28:46,800
'Jutro,

307
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:01,920
'Jutro, Spud,

308
00:29:02,120 --> 00:29:05,680
'Jutro, Gail, G, Houston,
Gospođo, - 'Jutro, Spud,

309
00:29:05,920 --> 00:29:08,320
Doručkuj s nama,

310
00:29:10,320 --> 00:29:14,920
Oprosti zbog sinoć, - Nema
veze, Spavala sam na kauču,

311
00:29:16,120 --> 00:29:19,960
Malo sam popio,
pa se... dogodilo,

312
00:29:20,200 --> 00:29:22,520
Ma bez brige, Događa se to,

313
00:29:22,720 --> 00:29:25,200
Čovjek se katkad
mora izdivljati,

314
00:29:25,400 --> 00:29:28,160
Ovoga bi katkad
trebalo utegnuti,

315
00:29:28,320 --> 00:29:31,720
Oprat ću plahtu,
- Ne, ne, Ja ću,

316
00:29:31,880 --> 00:29:35,960
Ne treba, - Nije mi teško,
- Ni meni, - Radije ću ja...

317
00:29:36,280 --> 00:29:40,240
Nije mi teško, - Ne...
- Plahta je moja!

318
00:29:52,880 --> 00:29:55,440
Zašto ne? - Jer je
to protuzakonito!

319
00:29:55,600 --> 00:29:59,080
Držanje za ruke? - Ne to!
- Onda me primi,

320
00:29:59,480 --> 00:30:03,320
<i>Sinoć si činio i mnogo više...
- To je protuzakonito!</i>

321
00:30:03,520 --> 00:30:07,200
Završit ću u
gajbi, bez jaja!

322
00:30:07,440 --> 00:30:11,120
Ma nećeš u zatvor,
- Tebi je to lako reći,

323
00:30:11,640 --> 00:30:14,680
Kad se opet
vidimo? - Nikada!

324
00:30:14,960 --> 00:30:18,320
Onda ću reći policiji,

325
00:30:20,280 --> 00:30:23,360
Dakle, vidimo se,

326
00:30:34,960 --> 00:30:37,160
Što sad?

327
00:30:37,360 --> 00:30:41,000
Šetnja, - Što?!
- Idemo u šetnju,

328
00:30:41,880 --> 00:30:45,000
Kamo? - Onamo,

329
00:30:45,560 --> 00:30:48,640
Ti to ozbiljno?!

330
00:31:19,840 --> 00:31:23,600
Što čekate?! - Tommy...

331
00:31:25,600 --> 00:31:29,600
Ovo nije prirodno...
- Priroda je divna!

332
00:31:30,600 --> 00:31:33,040
Svjež zrak!

333
00:31:33,240 --> 00:31:37,800
Znamo da patiš zbog Lizzy,
ali ne moraš nas nučiti,

334
00:31:38,120 --> 00:31:41,080
Niste li ponosni
što ste Škoti?

335
00:31:41,240 --> 00:31:43,480
Biti Škot je sranje!

336
00:31:43,600 --> 00:31:46,240
Mi smo najveće
smeće na svijetu!

337
00:31:46,360 --> 00:31:49,960
Najjadnije, bijedno,
puzavo smeće

338
00:31:50,120 --> 00:31:53,560
ikad izasrano
u civilizaciju!

339
00:31:53,640 --> 00:31:57,240
Svi mrze Engleze, Ja ne;
oni su samo drkadžije,

340
00:31:57,440 --> 00:32:00,520
Ali te su nas
drkadžije potlačile!

341
00:32:00,680 --> 00:32:04,160
Nismo mogli naći ni
poštene tlačitelje!

342
00:32:04,360 --> 00:32:07,120
Nama vladaju
istrošeni šupci!

343
00:32:07,280 --> 00:32:13,680
Govana do grla, stari! A
svjež zrak tu ne može pomoći!

344
00:32:21,960 --> 00:32:24,760
Žao mi je, stari,
- Stvarno...

345
00:32:26,760 --> 00:32:31,480
<i>Tada smo Spud, Sick Boy
i ja demokratski odlučili;</i>

346
00:32:31,600 --> 00:32:33,920
<i>vraćamo na heroin,</i>

347
00:32:34,200 --> 00:32:36,720
<i>Trebalo je oko 12 sati,</i>

348
00:32:37,000 --> 00:32:39,560
Paul Newman je zapravo
svijetu učinio uslugu...

349
00:32:39,720 --> 00:32:45,600
<i>Čini se lako, ali nije,
Pomislio bi, Ništa lakše;</i>

350
00:32:46,160 --> 00:32:50,600
<i>ali ovakav je život
zapravo vrlo naporan,</i>

351
00:33:08,480 --> 00:33:13,640
<i>Ursula Andress...
Savršena Bondova djevojka,</i>

352
00:33:13,720 --> 00:33:19,120
To svi kažu, Jasan izraz nje-
gove superiornosti nad nama,

353
00:33:19,560 --> 00:33:22,800
Lijepa, Egzotična, Vrlo seksi,

354
00:33:23,520 --> 00:33:26,880
Potpuno nedostupna
svima osim njemu,

355
00:33:27,840 --> 00:33:29,880
Sranje,

356
00:33:30,040 --> 00:33:35,200
Mislim, da je poševi jedan
od nas, dala bi nam svima!

357
00:33:46,920 --> 00:33:49,640
Znao sam da će to učiniti,

358
00:33:58,920 --> 00:34:02,680
<i>Lizzy je otišla,
Napucala me,</i>

359
00:34:04,320 --> 00:34:09,600
Zbog one snimke, Zbog Iggy
Popa i sličnih sranja,

360
00:34:10,640 --> 00:34:13,880
Rekla mi kud da se gonim,

361
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:18,160
<i>Rekao sam joj,
A da probamo ponovno?</i>

362
00:34:18,320 --> 00:34:21,000
Ali ne jebe me,

363
00:34:21,360 --> 00:34:25,120
<i>Honor Blackman,
Alias Pussy Galore,</i>

364
00:34:26,120 --> 00:34:29,600
Potpuno krivi nadimak!

365
00:34:30,240 --> 00:34:33,360
Ne bih ni s tvojim!

366
00:34:33,640 --> 00:34:36,280
Želim probati, Mark,

367
00:34:36,520 --> 00:34:41,240
Uvijek govoriš kako je fik-
sanje bolje od najbolje ševe,

368
00:34:44,760 --> 00:34:48,960
Daj! Odrastao sam,
Mogu sam odlučiti,

369
00:34:53,000 --> 00:34:55,360
Imam lovu,

370
00:34:58,080 --> 00:35:01,520
Osobnost, To je važno,

371
00:35:01,920 --> 00:35:05,560
Osobnost održava
vezu tijekom godina,

372
00:35:07,520 --> 00:35:11,280
Kao heroin, Hoću reći...

373
00:35:11,920 --> 00:35:15,280
Heroin ima super
jebenu osobnost...

374
00:35:28,120 --> 00:35:31,480
<i>Swanney kaže da moramo
poštovati Zdravstveno;</i>

375
00:35:31,640 --> 00:35:34,200
