376
00:35:34,360 --> 00:35:36,920
<i>Krali smo drogu,
recepte, prodavali ih,</i>

377
00:35:37,080 --> 00:35:39,880
<i>krivotvorili ih,
fotokopirali,</i>

378
00:35:40,040 --> 00:35:43,840
<i>uzimali drogu od oboljelih
od raka, alkića, staraca,</i>

379
00:35:44,000 --> 00:35:47,400
