dokonih domaćica,</i>

380
00:35:47,600 --> 00:35:51,080
<i>Morfij, diamorphine,
Cyclozine, Codeine, Temazepam,</i>

381
00:35:51,280 --> 00:35:56,160
<i>Nitrazepam, Phenomarbitone,
Metadon, Nalbuphine,</i>

382
00:35:56,360 --> 00:35:58,680
<i>Pethidine, Pentazocine,</i>

