386
00:36:07,720 --> 00:36:11,800
<i>Uzimali bismo i vitamin
C da je bio zabranjen,</i>

387
00:36:19,760 --> 00:36:23,240
Mogu se poslužiti
zahodom? Hvala,

388
00:36:34,760 --> 00:36:37,240
Ti si lud!

389
00:36:45,680 --> 00:36:48,880
A sada... Gubi se,

390
00:36:53,480 --> 00:36:57,000
<i>Ali uživanje
ne traje vječno...</i>

391
00:37:03,160 --> 00:37:06,080
