morao nešto reći,</i>

396
00:37:18,480 --> 00:37:20,000
Allison!

397
00:37:20,200 --> 00:37:22,760
Pomozite mi! - Smiri se!

398
00:37:23,000 --> 00:37:25,520
Sve će biti u redu,

399
00:37:25,680 --> 00:37:28,440
